@startuml
title Funds, Clearing, Settlement, and Merchant Payout
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam ArrowColor #4A5568
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #5B6B82
skinparam ActorBorderColor #5B6B82

legend right
|= Color |= System |
|<#FFF2CC>| Customer / Finance |
|<#E2F7E2>| Your store-side systems |
|<#CFE2FF>| Your backend / ACQP core |
|<#F4CCCC>| Alipay+ backend / reports |
|<#F5F5F5>| Ledger / bank / report record |
----
|<#C0392B>| Red arrows = Alipay+ API or report interactions |
|<#2E8B57>| Green arrows = internal ledger or payout actions |
endlegend

actor Customer #FFF2CC
participant "Store POS / App" as Store #E2F7E2
participant "Your Backend / ACQP" as ACQP #CFE2FF
participant "Alipay+ APIs" as AP #F4CCCC
database "Ledger DB" as Ledger #F5F5F5
participant "Reconciliation Service" as Recon #CFE2FF
participant "Reconciliation Reports" as Reports #F4CCCC
participant "Clearing Bank" as Bank #F5F5F5
participant "ACQP Settlement Account" as Acct #F5F5F5
participant "Merchant Settlement Engine" as MSE #CFE2FF
participant "Merchant / Store Bank Account" as StoreBank #F5F5F5

autonumber "S00"

Customer -> Store: Pay for order
Store -> ACQP: Create payment\n(paymentAmount / orderAmount,\nsettlement currency config)
ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: pay(...,\npaymentAmount,\nsettlementStrategy.settlementCurrency)
AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: payment accepted / final result
note over ACQP, AP
Official amount layers:
- paymentAmount = transaction amount
- settlementAmount / settlementQuote
  are returned on success when applicable
end note
ACQP -[#2E8B57]> Ledger: Book gross transaction\nand provisional receivable

Reports -[#C0392B]> Recon: T+1 transaction detail report
Reports -[#C0392B]> Recon: T+1 fee report
Reports -[#C0392B]> Recon: T+1 transaction summary report
Recon -[#2E8B57]> Ledger: Match transaction amount,\nsettlement amount, and fees

Reports -[#C0392B]> Bank: Settlement report / batch
Bank -[#2E8B57]> Acct: Net settlement funds\non agreed value date
Recon -[#2E8B57]> Ledger: Confirm net settlement amount,\nsettlement batch, value date

MSE -[#2E8B57]> Ledger: Apply merchant contract rule
note over MSE, Ledger
Official docs define ACQP-level settlement
and reconciliation facts.
Merchant payout is still your own
contract and finance rule.
end note
MSE -[#2E8B57]> StoreBank: Payout merchant / store funds

note over Recon, Reports
Official reconciliation set:
Transaction Detail Report,
Fee Report,
Transaction Summary Report,
Settlement Report.
These reports define ACQP-level
calculation inputs, not merchant payout policy.
end note
@enduml
